    <text id="B1043T">
        <front id="d2">
            <div1 type="summary" id="d3">
                <p>Jackson reports no criminal trials involving freedmen for the month of April.</p>
            </div1>
        </front>

        <body id="d4">
            <div1 type="letter" id="d5">
                <head>
                    Bureau <abbr expan="Refugees, Freedmen and Abandoned Lands">R. F. &amp; A.
                        L.</abbr><lb/><abbr expan="Sub-District">Sub. Dist.</abbr> Augusta &amp;
                    Highland
                    <name type="recipient"><abbr expan="Captain">Capt.</abbr> Garrick Mallery 43<hi
                            rend="super">rd</hi>
                        <abbr expan="United States Infantry">U.S.I.</abbr><lb/><abbr
                            expan="Acting Assistant Adjutant General">A. Asst.
                        Adj.Genl</abbr><lb/>Richmond</name>
                </head>

                <opener>
                    <dateline>
                        <date value="1867-05-01">May 1<hi rend="super">st</hi> 1867</date>
                        <name type="place">Staunton <abbr expan="Virginia">Va.</abbr></name>
                    </dateline>
                    <salute>Captain</salute>
                </opener>

                <p>In compliance with requirements of <abbr expan="Circular">Cir.</abbr> 10 <abbr
                        expan="Series">S.</abbr> 1866 <abbr
                        expan="Bureau of Refugees, Freedmen and Abandoned Lands">B. R. F. &amp;
                        A. L.</abbr> I have the honor to report that no Criminal Trials involving
                    the rights of Refugees or Freedmen have occurred since my assignment to this
                    District April 3<hi rend="super">d</hi>
                    <abbr expan="1867">/67</abbr></p>

                <p>I learn that in Highland county, since Refugees have been hardly dealt with at
                    courts held previously, but I have not been able to procure full details on
                    which to <unclear>provide</unclear> a report.</p>

                <closer>
                    <salute>
                        <abbr expan="Your obedient servant">Yr. obt. servt</abbr>
                    </salute>
                    <signed><hi rend="underline"><abbr expan="Thomas">Tho<hi rend="super"
                            >s</hi></abbr> P. Jackson</hi><lb/>Agent</signed>
                    <seg type="postscript">Through <abbr expan="Captain">Capt.</abbr>
                        <abbr expan="John">J.</abbr> A. McDonnell<lb/><abbr
                            expan="Sub Assistant Commissioner">Sub. Asst. Com<hi rend="super"
                        >r</hi></abbr> 9<hi rend="super">th</hi> District</seg>
                </closer>
            </div1>
        </body>
    </text>
